Alignment Channel										TYPE:General.AttackOption		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Channel Energy																																																																																							DESC:You can channel your divine energy to harm or heal outsiders that possess your chosen alignment subtype.																					STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:STRING|Chaos|Evil|Good|Law																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.117	BENEFIT:Instead of its normal effect, you can choose to have your ability to channel energy heal or harm outsiders of the chosen alignment subtype. You must make this choice each time you channel energy. If you choose to heal or harm creatures of the chosen alignment subtype, your channel energy has no effect on other creatures. The amount of damage healed or dealt and the DC to halve the damage is otherwise unchanged.
